{"tid":2434575,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國會暴動事件 首位川普閣員被逮捕","createTime":"2021-03-05T15:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T15:33:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"860c7d44114bd7d7eb690a0cb8d3c6e76bff1500","tid":2434575,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國聯邦調查局（FBI）當地時間4日逮捕了美國國務院前幕僚柯連（Federico Klein），指控他涉嫌參與1月6日美國國會暴動事件。柯連是第一位因美國國會暴動而被起訴的前美國總統川普內閣成員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n柯連於2016年進入川普進選團隊，並於2017年擔任西半球事務局（Bureau of Western Hemisphere Affairs）擔任特別助理，編入川普行政團隊。目前他是首位因美國暴動而被起訴的川普內閣成員。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3457659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3457659&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedW8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=d0781d7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3457659&h=5a451cb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3457659</a>"},{"pid":"0892b6a55a1eda5ce60ddd70dfa5f8c783cada12","tid":2434575,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0220bf4fb9aec965c5275171018ac8312a210185","tid":2434575,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}